data.text:
PBF artist Nick Gurewitch will be attending Webcomicon in Michigan! https://webcomicon.net/ August 3rd and 4th.

It seems we have regained full access to the PBF Facebook account! That sure was disturbing. Thank you to Ali Schlesinger, Alex Knott, Andrew Martilla, Eric Chang and many others for their help. Evil still lurks on FB, however. The latest menace seems to be a bot that automatically steals and posts.
